00:40:21.030 --> 00:40:23.700
He clearly says in
the introduction

00:40:23.700 --> 00:40:27.190
that there are a lot of books
and references by famous people

00:40:27.190 --> 00:40:30.170
who have said the
Casimir force is

00:40:30.170 --> 00:40:32.920
the manifestation of
the zero point energy.

00:40:32.920 --> 00:40:36.030
The fact that people have
observed the Casimir force

00:40:36.030 --> 00:40:40.290
means that h bar
omega over 2 is real.

00:40:43.640 --> 00:40:45.950
Those authors take
the opposite approach.

00:40:45.950 --> 00:40:49.060
They say this is just heuristic.

00:40:49.060 --> 00:40:49.980
It's convenient.

00:40:49.980 --> 00:40:51.830
You can get the correct result.

00:40:51.830 --> 00:40:55.130
But there is an
