00:40:55.130 --> 00:40:58.680
which gives exactly the same
result, which focuses only

00:40:58.680 --> 00:41:01.620
on pair wise interactions
between atoms,

00:41:01.620 --> 00:41:07.090
and it does not include any--
it doesn't make any reference

00:41:07.090 --> 00:41:10.450
to the zero point energy of
the electromagnetic field.

00:41:10.450 --> 00:41:13.800
So therefore, one, I would
agree with those authors

00:41:13.800 --> 00:41:17.450
that the conclusion
is there is absolutely

00:41:17.450 --> 00:41:23.260
